msgid ""
"QueAI gestiona módulos de IA empaquetados como contenedores Docker.\n"
"                Cada módulo es independiente, expone su propia UI y se instala con\n"
"                un click desde el Hub."
msgstr ""
"QueAI manages AI modules packaged as Docker containers.\n"
"                Each module is independent, exposes its own UI and installs\n"
"                with one click from the Hub."

msgid "Ver arquitectura →"
msgstr "See architecture →"

msgid "Instala tu primer módulo"
msgstr "Install your first module"

msgid ""
"En el Marketplace encuentras OCR, STT y TTS oficiales. Descárgalos,\n"
"                instálalos desde el Hub y empieza a usarlos en local."
msgstr ""
"The Marketplace ships official OCR, STT and TTS. Download them,\n"
"                install from the Hub and start running them locally."

msgid "Ir al Marketplace →"
msgstr "Open Marketplace →"

msgid "Crea tu propio plugin"
msgstr "Build your own plugin"

msgid ""
"Cualquier microservicio con un <code>manifest.json</code> y un\n"
"                <code>docker-compose.yml</code> puede ser un plugin de QueAI.\n"
"                Hay una plantilla lista para clonar."
msgstr ""
"Any microservice with a <code>manifest.json</code> and a\n"
"                <code>docker-compose.yml</code> can be a QueAI plugin.\n"
"                There's a template ready to clone."

